snippet.title: ⟁False Server - Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the game right now: 
https://sigmasuccour.itch.io/false-server

⟁False Server is a psychological, story-focused game about a game developer launching his discord server, while a pandemic is going on outside in the real world.
Discord Invite: https://discord.gg/hVVdm5Z

This is the trailer for the game's tech demo. You can download it from any of the following link: 
https://sigmasuccour.itch.io/false-server
https://gamejolt.com/games/FalseServer/506664
(only for Windows PCs) 

Game Engine: RPG Maker MV
Trailer BGM: 'Keep it Wavy' by Punch Deck
https://youtu.be/KgAhJ_4sFIc
